    <script>
    709+
    // Accordion functionality
    710+
    const accordionItems = document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-item');
    711+
    712+
    accordionItems.forEach(item => {
    713+
    const header = item.querySelector('.accordion-header');
    714+
    715+
    header.addEventListener('click', () => {
    716+
    // Close all other accordion items
    717+
    accordionItems.forEach(otherItem => {
    718+
    if (otherItem !== item && otherItem.classList.contains('active')) {
    719+
    otherItem.classList.remove('active');
    720+
    }
    721+
    });
    722+
    723+
    // Toggle active class
    724+
    item.classList.toggle('active');
    725+
    });
    726+
    });
    727+
    728+
    // Testimonial slider
    729+
    const testimonialContainer = document.querySelector('.testimonial-container');
    730+
    const sliderDots = document.querySelectorAll('.slider-dot');
    731+
    const testimonials = document.querySelectorAll('.testimonial');
    732+
    733+
    sliderDots.forEach((dot, index) => {
    734+
    dot.addEventListener('click', () => {
    735+
    // Update active dot
    736+
    sliderDots.forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
    737+
    dot.classList.add('active');
    738+
    739+
    // Slide to the selected testimonial
    740+
    testimonialContainer.scrollLeft = index * testimonialContainer.clientWidth;
    741+
    });
    742+
    });
    743+
    744+
    // Auto slide testimonials every 5 seconds
    745+
    let currentSlide = 0;
    746+
    747+
    function autoSlide() {
    748+
    currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % testimonials.length;
    749+
    750+
    // Update active dot
    751+
    sliderDots.forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
    752+
    sliderDots[currentSlide].classList.add('active');
    753+
    754+
    // Slide to the next testimonial
    755+
    testimonialContainer.scrollLeft = currentSlide * testimonialContainer.clientWidth;
    756+
    }
    757+
    758+
    let slideInterval = setInterval(autoSlide, 5000);
    759+
    760+
    // Pause auto slide when user interacts with testimonials
    761+
    testimonialContainer.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
    762+
    clearInterval(slideInterval);
    763+
    });
    764+
    765+
    testimonialContainer.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
    766+
    slideInterval = setInterval(autoSlide, 5000);
    767+
    });
    768+
    769+
    // Mobile menu for dropdown
    770+
    const dropdowns = document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown');
    771+
    772+
    if (window.innerWidth <= 768) {
    773+
    dropdowns.forEach(dropdown => {
    774+
    dropdown.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    775+
    e.preventDefault();
    776+
    dropdown.classList.toggle('active');
    777+
    });
    778+
    });
    779+
    }
    780+
    </script>
